{
  "stem": "18470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We really don't know who did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to presume there was a Nazi party in Oberwesel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that while I was not aware of many Nazis in Oberwesel, Nazis being people in uniform, there were Nazi sympathizers all over town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there was a great deal to be gotten from the confiscation of Jewish property.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For example, my grandfather was compelled to sell our home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what happened was he sold the home to a Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Knopf, and for a ridiculous price of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The money was, I think it was 12,000 marks, for a home plus a garden.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The money was then deposited in the local bank, which was then confiscated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you could not use the money that--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you had so-- so ostensibly received from the sale-- from the sale of the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was deposited in the bank, and then it was closed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The account was blocked is the word, [NON-ENGLISH] was blocked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the systematization-- the systematic impoverishment that took place from '36 on, by limiting trade, by-- one of the reasons my father had to illegally go to the back country to trade with farmers is because he was not allowed to do business.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if you can't do business, and you can't earn income, and if you couldn't emigrate in a timely way, which was the pressure to build up then to get you out, you starve to death.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And ultimately, that's what happened to the Jews who were unable to emigrate, like my grandfather and my aunts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were herded together in a Judenhaus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had to vacate the residences where they were, those that had not been deported, those that had not emigrated.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
